N = natural numbers = {0,1,2,3,...}
Z = integers = {...,-3,-2,-1,0,1,2,3,...}
Z⁺ = positive integers = {1,2,3,...}
R = set of real numbers
R+ = set of positive real numbers
C = set of complex numbers.
Q = set of rational numbers

